        "boundaries": "Reads from MongoDB, writes to PostgreSQL. Runs as a separate process (not in the request path). Uses PostgreSQL advisory locks to prevent concurrent migration runs."
      },
      {
        "name": "VerificationService",
        "responsibility": "Compares data between MongoDB and PostgreSQL to verify migration correctness. Runs count checks, random-sample deep comparisons, and checksum verification. Produces a parity report.",
